invalid type: string "Rajiv Gandhi Intl. Stadium, Hyderabad SRH's home ground became the most feared batting venue in 2024. The flat pitch combined with heavy evening dew makes chasing almost a formality in night matches. Travis Head's 191.6 SR and Abhishek Sharma's 188.3 SR are products of this ground. In 2024, SRH scored 250+ twice here. Bowling first is almost always the correct call.", expecte